<td valign="top" align="left" style="border-left: solid 5px #f0f0f0;;padding:0px 5px 0px 15px;">




<strong>Studio Album, released in 2006</strong><br><br>

<strong>Songs / Tracks Listing</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">1. Title (0:33)<br>2. Palace of Mirrors (3:40)<br>3. A Corporate Merger (8:14)<br>4. The Terrible Beautypower of Meow (4:01)<br>5. Colossal Risk (4:36)<br>6. The Unfolding Pause On The Thresholdm (4:16)<br>7. Smuggled Mutation (4:43)<br>8. Six Hands (1:08)<br>9. The Debutante (2:40)<br>10. Flower Garden of An Evil Man (6:12)<br>11. Those Who Know... (5:16)<br>12. Palace of Mirrors Reprise (6:16)<br>13. The Return (6:19)<br><br>Total Time: 57:54</p>

